comments: This was the winning one of two performances of the same song competing for Sweden's entry in same year's Eurovision Song Contest, with En gång i Stockholm being the other. In the ESC, it shared the 13th place with Netherlands' Annie Palmen 's "Een speeldoos", Norway's Anita Thallaug 's "Solvherv" and Finland's Muistojeni laulu (all 0 points) - the only time Sweden scored no points in that contest.

name: En gång i Stockholm
comments: This was one of two performances of the same song performed there. Monica Zetterlund's version won and became Sweden's entry in the Eurovision Song Contest of that year.
